import { createContext } from 'react'

interface IEthFLIPTokenMarketDataValues {
  prices?: number[][]

  marketcaps?: number[][]
  volumes?: number[][]

const IEthFLIPMarketData = createContext<IEthFLIPTokenMarketDataValues>({})
